  "title": "How to change password on the Website?",
  "html_content": "<main class=\"SuperHubDoc3Z-1XSVTg-Q1 rm-Guides\" id=\"content\"><div class=\"SuperHubDoc-container2RY1FPE4Ewze rm-Container rm-Container_flex\"><article class=\"SuperHubDoc-article3ArTrEavUTKg rm-Article rm-Guides-SuperHub\"><div class=\"grid-container-fluid\" id=\"content-container\"><section class=\"content-body grid-75\"><div class=\"rm-Markdown markdown-body rm-Markdown markdown-body ng-non-bindable\" data-testid=\"RDMD\" style=\"margin-left:31px\"><h2 class=\"heading heading-2 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"follow-these-instruction-below-to-change-password-on-the-website\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Follow these instruction below to change password on the Website:</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Follow these instruction below to change password on the Website:\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#follow-these-instruction-below-to-change-password-on-the-website\"></a></h2>\n<p><strong>Step 1. Click on the drop-down arrow next to your account name at the top right-hand side of your screen and select \"Change Password\".</strong></p>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/da5ecfc-passchange1.png\" title=\"passchange1.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<p><strong>Step 2. Fill in all required fields including Current Password, New Password, and Verify Password</strong>.</p>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/3b91c33-passchange2.png\" title=\"passchange2.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<blockquote class=\"callout callout_info\" theme=\"ðŸ“˜\"><span class=\"callout-icon\">ðŸ“˜</span><h3 class=\"heading heading-3 header-scroll\"><div class=\"heading-anchor anchor waypoint\" id=\"notice\"></div><div class=\"heading-text\">Notice</div><a aria-label=\"Skip link to Notice\" class=\"heading-anchor-icon fa fa-regular fa-anchor\" href=\"#notice\"></a></h3><ul>\n<li>When filling in New Password field, please follow the system suggested conditions to create a strong password.</li>\n<li>When verifying your new password, please type in exactly the same password just filled in above. Otherwise, the system will not allow to change the password.</li>\n</ul></blockquote>\n<p><strong>Step 3. Click on \"Change Password\".</strong></p>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/468a07a-passchange3.png\" title=\"passchange3.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span>\n<ul>\n<li>After finishing the last step, the system will pop-up a notification of \"Password Changed successfully\".</li>\n</ul>\n<span aria-label=\"Expand image\" class=\"img lightbox closed\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><span class=\"lightbox-inner\"><img alt=\"1920\" class=\"img\" height=\"auto\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"../assets_user_guide/d7bda7b-passchange4.png\" title=\"passchange4.png\" width=\"auto\" style=\"max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto; max-width:100%; height:auto;\"/></span></span></div><div class=\"UpdatedAt\"><p class=\"DateLine\"><i class=\"icon icon-watch\"></i>Updated<!-- --> <!-- -->about 1 month ago<!-- --> </p></div><hr class=\"NextStepsDivider\"/></section><section class=\"content-toc grid-25\"></section></div><div class=\"ModalWrapper\" id=\"tutorialmodal-root\"></div></article></div></main>",
